egalArgumentException ex) {\\n            return Validated.invalid(prefixedProperty, value, \\\"must be a valid URL\\\", InvalidReason.MALFORMED, ex);\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static String prefixedProperty(MeterRegistryConfig config, String property) {\\n        return config.prefix() + '.' + property;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777693622753}, {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_7dQh2Z4qMvNi114hUghUIskA|fc_07205cd0164c6c450169f573b66d5881a0a133e2f448137d7b\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"tests/src/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/src/test/java/io_micrometer/micrometer_core/ExecutorServiceMetricsTest.java\\ntests/src/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/src/test/java/io_micrometer/micrometer_core/FileDescriptorMetricsTest.java\\ntests/src/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/src/test/java/io_micrometer/micrometer_core/HazelcastIMapAdapterTest.java\\ntests/src/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/src/test/java/io_micrometer/micrometer_core/Micrometer_coreTest.java\\ntests/src/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/src/test/java/io_micrometer/micrometer_core/ProcessorMetricsTest.java\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777693622753}, {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_4lHeVLgygiCeRJtEJEdfRdxW|fc_07205cd0164c6c450169f573b66d6081a0805e61b40cef3060\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/main/extracted/io/micrometer/core/instrument/config/validate/DurationValidator.java\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/io.micrometer/micrometer-core/1.8.2/main/extracted/io/micrometer/core/instrument/config/validate/PropertyValidator.java\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/i